{"tid":1319162,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"遞信辭職後嗰一個月會點過？","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T09:35:06.000Z","uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"39d1ba9466718b856e0045a47153a032bd962776","tid":1319162,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"準備好遞信，諗緊嚟緊一個月點過好，唔可以遲到公司會扣錢"},{"pid":"cdefb49b500a23bfdab05e3ddbd02e972347bf95","tid":1319162,"uid":266336,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"遲開 早/準時收<br />\n收左唔接電話 咩都唔理<br />\n同事有難 唔幫 唔關我事一於少理<br />\n可以拎假就盡拎咁上下"},{"pid":"0754d7092e207aa6f3147b5b6cd09bdd30fa1da6","tid":1319162,"uid":62996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"掉哂啲野比接手同事跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩下手機又一日"},{"pid":"034d4604c120491627a8bc5bc566e53295662cff","tid":1319162,"uid":41818,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"backup自己d料 教壞下手 ot不合作運動"},{"pid":"e444004cc6dd062d900d5489b2b771a2808c6dca","tid":1319162,"uid":50641,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:13:52.000Z","msg":"以前試過<br />\n計下仲有幾個假 扣晒假期<br />\n之後返工日子就日日約章工作<br />\n遲到早走 收工熄公司電話 咩都唔撚理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bb8a1d16c367662a0779f41a615c2876f85927","tid":1319162,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"睇你同公司係咪和平分手"},{"pid":"d747a8eda11fcbc54be71a41fa23f5accb3cca52","tid":1319162,"uid":132930,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"日日遲到早走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n按章工作, 文件急到瀨屎都不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打下機, 上下網咁又日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留低的, 都是一份心意, 所以留了一堆不夠時間做的蘇州屎俾下手/其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315b723962d826f53ea7c0a485cba640390c8c1a","tid":1319162,"uid":29081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"好似林奠依家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6125757e8db3c4a8c70a7d09ecb6611d4a2707","tid":1319162,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"各位佢唔可以遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但可以遲開 ，你都知每日做野前有好多野要準備，包括個人心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec600639bb79b7791c27118b1f93884d0590953","tid":1319162,"uid":29081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"315b723962d826f53ea7c0a485cba640390c8c1a","tid":1319162,"uid":29081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:19:50.000Z","msg":"好似林奠依家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"日日唔見影<br />\n問咩都係罐頭答覆<br />\n著到送殯咁去annual dinner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb28b97c686d669af24d7cb56412a42109a15e0","tid":1319162,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d8b9fd818eb8911dfcb5315473ff4026339ff3d","tid":1319162,"uid":181997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"巴打做邊行先？<br />\n我之前就日日準時返工打咭<br />\n開完早會，幫手開門嘅嘢<br />\n同經理講去廁所<br />\n去機鋪/網吧打機，打兩三個鐘返鋪頭<br />\n夠鐘就去食飯，不過一定要準時，唔好阻下更食飯同事 <br />\n等到個個食完飯，再同經理講去廁所<br />\n同女朋去食飯，食到差唔多就返鋪頭打咭收工"},{"pid":"d4552e4301119abf4cea2806f6c478e8d44d8e58","tid":1319162,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"唔點做野 留比下手啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e35b0f37eeee1e0f842f402a1d634e2a870b60",