love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383c5ca59516d992cc9aef58f2958c6020030a14","tid":1319162,"uid":112183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fca2c2873f024821224da3d451e9dbdde439ea0","tid":1319162,"uid":254568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"上個月遞信,,呢個月走人,日日遲到早退咁,一有機會就出去蛇王,將手頭上嘅野做亂佢,等上司之後執到仆街<br />\n利申:同個上司唔妥,以前個上司一有機會就質我食死貓,依家我一有機會就駁/屌 7佢"}]}